%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor FW as Firmware
  participant API as Go API (REST)
  participant DB as Postgres/Timescale

  FW->>API: GET /api/bootstrap?imei=...\nHeader: x-api-key
  API->>DB: Lookup device by IMEI\n+ installation + beneficiary\n+ vfd_model (if assigned)
  DB-->>API: device + context + credential bundle
  API-->>FW: 200 JSON bootstrap\nprimary_broker.endpoints[]\npublish_topics[]\nsubscribe_topics[]\n(optional) govt_broker
  Note over API,FW: API may also set header X-Device-JWT for device-scoped auth helpers

  FW->>FW: Pick broker URL from primary_broker.endpoints[]\nPrefer mqtts:// when available
